@Comment:	Time is 0:09
@Comment:	This mealtime is rather lengthy (almost 23 minutes long) and most of the time Chi , MOT and MAL are engaged in conversation regarding proper table manners , the food that they are eating (at one point Chi inquires as to the amount of fat in the bread) and the neighborhood kids. Both Mot and MAL seem relaxed with one another and patient with Chi. It seems that there is another child at the dinner table as well , but this child doesn't talk much. Towards the end of the tape two other adults come in and out of the house. It seems as if the man is fixing a car outside.
